				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\begin{array}{rcl}H & = & V\sum _{n}({C}_{n}{C}_{n+1}^{\ast }+{C}_{n}^{\ast }{C}_{n+1})\\  &  & +\chi \sum _{n}(|{C}_{n}{|}^{2}|{C}_{n+1}{|}^{2}+|{C}_{n}{|}^{4}).\end{array}$$\end{document}H=V∑n(CnCn+1⁎+Cn⁎Cn+1)+χ∑n(|Cn|2|Cn+1|2+|Cn|4).

In addition, our system obeys the staggered-unstaggered symmetry: Equation (1) is invariant under the transformation \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
